cnVlanPortMemberTable.name: cnVlanPortMemberTable
cnVlanPortMemberTable.description: The VLAN port membership configuration table. This table contains membership information pertaining to the ports belonging to a VLAN.

cnVlanPortMemberEntry.name: cnVlanPortMemberEntry
cnVlanPortMemberEntry.description: An entry containing VLAN membership information for a particular port. Entries are added by specifying the cnVlanPortMemberCard, cnVlanPortMemberPort, cnVlanPortMemberVID, and the cnVlanPortMemberIngressType. Entries are deleted simply by setting the cnVlanPortMemberStatus object to destroy.

cnVlanPortMemberCard.name: cnVlanPortMemberCard
cnVlanPortMemberCard.description: The card number for this port in the VLAN.

cnVlanPortMemberPort.name: cnVlanPortMemberPort
cnVlanPortMemberPort.description: The port number for this port in the VLAN.

cnVlanPortMemberVID.name: cnVlanPortMemberVID
cnVlanPortMemberVID.description: The VLAN ID of which this port is a member.

cnVlanPortMemberStatus.name: cnVlanPortMemberStatus
cnVlanPortMemberStatus.description: The current status of the entry. Entries may be added by specifying a value of createAndGo, and removed by setting the status to destroy.

cnVlanPortMemberIngressType.name: cnVlanPortMemberIngressType
cnVlanPortMemberIngressType.description: The method used to classify ingress frames on this port into this VLAN. The allowed values are specific to the cnVlanType of the VLAN as follows: byPort: pvid or tag byProtocolId: pvid, tag, or protocolId Allowable values may also be restricted by the VLAN capabilities of this port.

cnVlanPortMemberDynamic.name: cnVlanPortMemberDynamic
cnVlanPortMemberDynamic.description: The value for this object indicates whether the switch learned this port's VLAN membership dynamically.

cnVlanPortMemberIfIndex.name: cnVlanPortMemberIfIndex
cnVlanPortMemberIfIndex.description: The value for this object identifies the instance of the ifIndex object, defined in MIB-II, for the interface corresponding to this port and VLAN. If no such entry exists, the value 0 may be returned.

cnVlanPortMemberRing.name: cnVlanPortMemberRing
cnVlanPortMemberRing.description: The ring number for this port if this VLAN uses source route or source route transparent bridging.

cnVlanENETMgt.name: cnVlanENETMgt
cnVlanENETMgt.description: VID of the Ethernet management VLAN. The null VID indicates that an Ethernet management VLAN is not configured.

cnVlanTRMgt.name: cnVlanTRMgt
cnVlanTRMgt.description: VID of the Token Ring management VLAN. The null VID indicates that an Token Ring management VLAN is not configured.
